snippet.title: Clusterduck now available on the App Store and Google Play
snippet.description:
Download NOW on the App Store and Google Play: https://ppok.me/clusterduck

These ducks have gone absolutely bonkers. CLUSTERDUCK is about hatching as many ducks as possible. As more ducks hatch, the more strange things happen...
